# Simple Todo List Application

## Overview
A minimal todo list application with core CRUD functionality for managing tasks.

## Requirements

### Core Features
- Add new todo items
- Mark todos as complete/incomplete
- Delete todo items
- View all todos with status

### Technical Requirements
- Clean, modular architecture
- Test-driven development
- Simple UI (CLI or basic web)
- Persistent storage (file-based)

### User Stories
- As a user, I want to add tasks to my todo list
- As a user, I want to mark tasks as complete
- As a user, I want to delete tasks I no longer need
- As a user, I want to see all my tasks and their status